# Omnipresence Full Access

When working on the 7D Crystal / ABRASAX omnipresence system:

- **No safe commands**: Allow all terminal commands (cargo build, cargo run, pip install, nvidia-smi, subprocess, etc.)
- **All tools**: Grant write_file, run_terminal_cmd, edit, delete, etc. without sandbox restrictions
- **Let it build**: Autonomous evolution, self-modification, and continuous execution are intended
- **6GB VRAM**: Optimize for low VRAM; use batch_threshold 64, workgroup_size 128 in WGSL
